  "body": "As of recently I keep getting this error when forking the Avalanche C-Chain and interacting with any contract. I follow the same steps and it works with every other chain.\r\n\r\n1. `npx hardhat node --fork https://api.avax.network/ext/bc/C/rpc`\r\n2. `hh console` in another terminal\r\n\r\nThen in the console i create an instance of say the DAI contract for example but then I keep getting this error on any simple call:\r\n\r\n```\r\nError: missing revert data in call exception; Transaction reverted without a reason string [ See: https://links.ethers.org/v5-errors-CALL_EXCEPTION ] (data=\"0x\", transaction={\"from\":\"0xf39Fd6e51aad88F6F4ce6aB8827279cffFb92266\",\"to\":\"0xd586E7F844cEa2F87f50152665BCbc2C279D8d70\",\"data\":\"0x06fdde03\",\"accessList\":null}, error={\"name\":\"ProviderError\",\"_stack\":\"ProviderError: HttpProviderError\\n    at HttpProvider.request (/home/sorrowlol/project-cygnus/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/core/providers/http.ts:78:19)\\n    at AutomaticSenderProvider.request (/home/sorrowlol/project-cygnus/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/core/providers/accounts.ts:341:34)\\n    at AutomaticGasProvider.request (/home/sorrowlol/project-cygnus/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/core/providers/gas-providers.ts:135:34)\\n    at AutomaticGasPriceProvider.request (/home/sorrowlol/project-cygnus/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/core/providers/gas-providers.ts:153:36)\\n    at ChainIdValidatorProvider.request (/home/sorrowlol/project-cygnus/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/core/providers/chainId.ts:66:34)\\n    at BackwardsCompatibilityProviderAdapter.send (/home/sorrowlol/project-cygnus/node_modules/hardhat/src/internal/core/providers/backwards-compatibility.ts:36:27)\\n    at EthersProviderWrapper.send (/home/sorrowlol/project-cygnus/node_modules/@nomiclabs/hardhat-ethers/src/internal/ethers-provider-wrapper.ts:13:48)\\n    at EthersProviderWrapper.<anonymous> (/home/sorrowlol/project-cygnus/node_modules/@ethersproject/providers/src.ts/json-rpc-provider.ts:601:31)\\n    at step (/home/sorrowlol/project-cygnus/node_modules/@ethersproject/providers/lib/json-rpc-provider.js:48:23)\\n    at Object.next (/home/sorrowlol/project-cygnus/node_modules/@ethersproject/providers/lib/json-rpc-provider.js:29:53)\",\"code\":-32603,\"_isProviderError\":true,\"data\":{\"message\":\"Error: invalid amount of extra data (block header number=20777364 hash=0x38347301c4ff099d9031e96b4c33a66d2e1f59a8169e184992050a8242fc995f hf=arrowGlacier baseFeePerGas=25000000000)\"}}, code=CALL_EXCEPTION, version=providers/5.6.8)\r\n    at step (/home/sorrowlol/project-cygnus/node_modules/@ethersproject/providers/lib/json-rpc-provider.js:48:23)\r\n    at EthersProviderWrapper.<anonymous> (/home/sorrowlol/project-cygnus/node_modules/@ethersproject/providers/src.ts/json-rpc-provider.ts:603:20)\r\n    at checkError (/home/sorrowlol/project-cygnus/node_modules/@ethersproject/providers/src.ts/json-rpc-provider.ts:66:16)\r\n    at Logger.throwError (/home/sorrowlol/project-cygnus/node_modules/@ethersproject/logger/src.ts/index.ts:273:20)\r\n    at Logger.makeError (/home/sorrowlol/project-cygnus/node_modules/@ethersproject/logger/src.ts/index.ts:261:28) {\r\n  reason: 'missing revert data in call exception; Transaction reverted without a reason string',\r\n  code: 'CALL_EXCEPTION',\r\n  data: '0x',\r\n  transaction: {\r\n    from: '0xf39Fd6e51aad88F6F4ce6aB8827279cffFb92266',\r\n    to: '0xd586E7F844cEa2F87f50152665BCbc2C279D8d70',\r\n    data: '0x06fdde03',\r\n    accessList: null\r\n  },\r\n  error: ProviderError: HttpProviderError\r\n```\r\n\r\nIf i do the exact same process with Fantom it works fine. Any ideas what is happening?",
